ports.behavior:
forward Policy
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from Policy
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from EmailBodyAndHeader
assign Level.High if Level.High from Policy
assign Level.High if Level.High from EmailBodyAndHeader

forward BobPubKey
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from BobPubKey
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from EmailBodyAndHeader
assign Level.High if Level.High from BobPubKey
assign Level.High if Level.High from EmailBodyAndHeader

forward EmailBodyEncryptedAndHeaderAndBobPriveteKey
assign Level.High if LevelBeforeEncryption.High from EmailBodyEncryptedAndHeaderAndBobPriveteKey
assign Level.Low if LevelBeforeEncryption.Low from EmailBodyEncryptedAndHeaderAndBobPriveteKey

forward BobPrivateKey
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from BobPrivateKey
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from Policy
assign Level.High if Level.High from BobPrivateKey
assign Level.High if Level.High from Policy

forward BobPrivateKey
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from BobPrivateKey
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from EmailBodyEncryptedAndHeader
assign Level.High if Level.High from BobPrivateKey
assign Level.High if Level.High from EmailBodyEncryptedAndHeader

forward EmailBodyHeaderAndBobPubKey
assign LevelBeforeEncryption.High if Level.High from EmailBodyHeaderAndBobPubKey
assign LevelBeforeEncryption.Low if Level.Low from EmailBodyHeaderAndBobPubKey
unset Level.High
set Level.Low
